---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About AI Tools HQ - Our Mission & Story"
  description="Learn about AI Tools HQ, the curated directory helping creators and teams discover the best AI tools for their workflow."
>
  <main class="about-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>About AI Tools HQ</h1>
      <p>Helping you navigate the AI revolution</p>
    </header>

    <section class="content">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        The AI landscape is exploding. Every week, dozens of new tools launch promising to revolutionize
        how we work. But which ones actually deliver? That's where we come in.
      </p>
      <p>
        AI Tools HQ is a curated directory of the best AI tools for creators, developers, marketers,
        and teams. We test, review, and compare tools so you don't have to waste time on ones that don't work.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Curate</strong> – We handpick tools that actually solve problems</li>
        <li><strong>Review</strong> – Honest assessments based on real-world testing</li>
        <li><strong>Compare</strong> – Side-by-side comparisons to help you choose</li>
        <li><strong>Update</strong> – Fresh content as the AI landscape evolves</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Standards</h2>
      <p>
        Every tool in our directory meets our quality bar. We evaluate based on:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Actual usefulness (not just hype)</li>
        <li>User experience and ease of use</li>
        <li>Pricing transparency and value</li>
        <li>Customer support and reliability</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Some links on AI Tools HQ are affiliate links. This means we may earn a commission if you
        sign up through our links – at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the site running
        and continue providing free, honest reviews.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our reviews are never influenced by affiliate relationships. If a tool isn't good, we'll tell you.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-box">
      <h2>Have a tool to suggest?</h2>
      <p>Know an AI tool we should review? We'd love to hear from you.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .page-header p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content ul {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .cta-box {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-box h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-box p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    background: var(--accent-primary);
    color: var(--bg-primary);
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-secondary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-page {
      padding: 7rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
